events.name: North Carolina Tar Heels at South Carolina Gamecocks

headlines.description: Mike Davis ran 75 yards for a touchdown, Connor Shaw and Dylan Thompson each threw long scoring passes and All-American Jadeveon Clowney helped No. 6 South Carolina beat North Carolina 27-10 on Thursday night.

events.name: USC Trojans at Hawai'i Rainbow Warriors

headlines.description: Justin Davis ran for 74 yards and a touchdown, and No. 24 USC's defense picked up for its shaky offense, masking mixed performances by battling quarterbacks Cody Kessler and Max Wittek in a 30-13 win over Hawaii on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: USC's defense steals show vs. Hawaii

events.name: Indiana State Sycamores at Indiana Hoosiers

headlines.description: Indiana's Nate Sudfeld threw four touchdown passes, and Tevin Coleman rushed for 169 yards and two more TDs in Thursday night's record-breaking 73-35 victory over Indiana State.
headlines.shortLinkText: Indiana puts up 73 points in rout of Indiana St.

events.name: Rutgers Scarlet Knights at Fresno State Bulldogs

headlines.description: Derek Carr threw his fifth touchdown pass on the opening play of overtime and Fresno State stopped a 2-point try on the next possession to beat Rutgers 52-51 in the season opener Thursday night.
